<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَفِي نَحْوِ صَخْرٍ، وَأَحْوَاضٍ، وأَرْضٍ تَنَجَّسَتْ بِمَائِعٍ -وَلَوْ مِنْ كَلْبٍ أَوْ خِنْزِيرٍ-: مُكَاثَرَتُها بِمَاءٍ حَتَّى يَذْهَبَ لَوْنُ النَّجَاسَةِ وَرِيحُهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مَا لَمْ يَعْجِزْ عَنْ إِذْهَابِهِمَا، أَوْ إِذْهَابِ أَحَدِهِمَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَوْ لَمْ يَزَلِ المَاءُ فِيهِمَا،<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> فِي بَوْلِ الغُلَامِ، وَفِي الأَرْضِ وَنَحْوِهَا، فَيَطْهُرَانِ مَعَ بَقَاءِ المَاءِ عَلَيْهِمَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا تَطْهُرُ أَرْضٌ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- بِشَمْسٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَرِيحٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَجَفَافٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا نَجَاسَةٌ:</span> بِنَارٍ، فَرَمَادُهَا نَجِسٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَطْهُرُ خَمْرَةٌ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- انْقَلَبَتْ خَلًّا بِنَفْسِهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- أَوْ بِنَقْلٍ لَا لِقَصْدِ التَّخْلِيلِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَدَنُّهَا مِثْلُهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ خَفِيَتْ نَجَاسَةٌ:</span> غَسَلَ حَتَّى يَتَيَقَّنَ غَسْلَهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>